                  <div class="section-media-wall--list_description_origin_text">
                    I am very impressed with my yarbo and the yarbo team! After lots of live events and Q&amp;A sessions
                    I decided to purchase mine this summer for my elderly grandparents. Today was the first real
                    snowfall since set up and I am very pleased. Yes there were a few, and still are, some glitches but
                    overall very impressive. It made robotic snow blower all worth it to know my grandparents are
                    sitting in the comfort of their home while I watch yarbo clear their driveway from my house on my
                    phone. The yarbo team has been awesome with answering any questions/helping with tech support too.
                    Thank you yarbo and keep up the great work!
                  </div>
